                    <msContents>
                        <summary>This is a versified work in 220 couplets on definitions of Arabic words into Persian, 
                            corresponding couplets to Persian poetical and metrical measures. The number of couplets is recorded differently in the references.
                            This work has been used to teach Arabic in Iran, India and Turkey as lately as the recent centuries. It has been printed several times in Iran.
                        </summary>
                        <msItem>
                            <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                            <note type="content-genre">Dictionary</note>
                            <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">Niṣāb al-Ṣibyān</title>
                            <title xml:lang="per">نصاب الصبیان</title>
                            <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="alt"></title>
                            <title xml:lang="per" type="alt"></title>
                            <author key="no2006071896‏" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/56368539">
                                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">‎Farāhī, Abū Naṣr Muḥammad Badr al-Dīn‏‏</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per" type="standard">فراهی، ابونصر محمد بدرالدین</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Abū Naṣr Farāhī, Masʿūd bin Abī Bakr (640 Qamarī/1242)</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per"  type="alt">ابونصر فراهی، مسعود بن ابی بکر (۶۴۰ ق/۱۲۴۲م)</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per" type="alt"></persName>
                                <addName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="laqab"></addName>
                                <addName xml:lang="per" type="laqab"></addName>
                                <addName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="kunyah"></addName>
                                <addName xml:lang="per" type="kunyah"></addName>
                                <addName xml:lang="per" type="khitab"/>
                                <addName xml:lang="per" type="nisbah"/>
                            </author>
                            <note> 
                            </note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="per">… بدانکه این کتاب مشتمل است بر ده نوع علم. اول علم لغت و دویم علم… سیم علم کیمیا چهارم علم معرفت انساب… 
                            </incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="per">… باد اندر جوار رحمت حق/پدر و مادر و معلم ما.
                            </explicit>
                            <colophon xml:lang="per">تمام شد کتاب نصاب الصبیان فی تاریخ شهر جمیدی الثانی ثمانیة سبعین الف.
                            </colophon>
